txt.en: Anborn can be found in the keep at Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should speak with Anborn.
Yambahul can be found somewhere in Southern Ithilien.\n\nYou should defeat Yambahul.
'You continue to impress me with your skills. Yambahul's defeat will boost my mens' spirits in these difficult days. Good work.'
The bounty notice reads: \n\n'Rangers, we are in need of one of you to defeat Yambahul, a vile Haradrim chieftain. Speak with Anborn if you plan to accept this mission.'
A bounty notice asks you to seek out Anborn who has information about Yambahul, a vile Haradrim chieftain.

You ask Anborn about the bounty notice.\n\n'You wish to help our cause? Very well. I do not speak ill of your abilities as a warrior, but do take note, Yambahul is no ordinary foe. He is a high ranking chieftain and commands vast numbers. It will not be an easy fight.'
Anborn can be found in the keep at Bâr Húrin.\n\nYou should speak with Anborn.
